==2010年冬季奧運會==
===諾達爾·庫瑪麗塔什維利===
{{main|諾達爾·庫瑪麗塔什維利}}

2010年2月12日，在[[2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會開幕式|2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會開幕式]]舉行前數小時，代表[[格魯吉亞|格魯吉亞]]的雪橇手[[諾達爾·庫瑪麗塔什維利|諾達爾·庫瑪麗塔什維利]]在滑行中心賽道練習期間以時速143.3公里滑行，在16號彎位失控並飛出雪橇撞上鐵柱，<ref>{{Cite news|title = Luge Crash at the Olympics|newspaper = New York Times|location = New York, NY|publisher = Arthur O. Sulzberger, Jr.|date = 2010-02-12|url = http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2010/02/12/sports/olympics/LUGEDEATH.html|accessdate = 2010-02-16|archive-date = 2018-03-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180323154406/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2010/02/12/sports/olympics/LUGEDEATH.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="nytimes">{{cite news | last = Branch | first = John | coauthors = Jonathan Abrams | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/13/sports/olympics/13luge.html?hp=&pagewanted=print | title = Luge Athlete's Death Casts Pall Over Games | publisher = ''[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]'' | date = 2010-02-12 | accessdate = 2010-06-20 | archive-date = 2015-06-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150623084435/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/13/sports/olympics/13luge.html?hp=&pagewanted=print | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last = Bryant|first = Howard|coauthors = Bonnie D. Ford|url = http://sports.espn.go.com/olympics/winter/2010/news/story?id=4909034|title = Kumaritashvili killed in luge training|publisher = [[ESPN|ESPN]]|date = 2010-02-13|accessdate = 2010-06-20|archive-date = 2016-01-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160130104002/http://sports.espn.go.com/olympics/winter/2010/news/story?id=4909034|dead-url = no}}</ref>送院後搶救無效並於同日宣佈不治。<ref name=death>{{cite news|last=Bell|first=Terry|url=http://www.globaltvcalgary.com/story.html?id=2556532|title=Georgia's minister of sport pleads for a full investigation after luger's death|date=2010-02-12|publisher=Canwest News Service|accessdate=2010-02-12}}{{Dead link}}</ref>這是[[1992年冬季奧運會|1992年冬季奧運會]]後首次有運動員在冬季奧運會練習期間死亡，而庫瑪麗塔什維利也是繼[[1964年冬季奧林匹克運動會|1964年]]代表英國的{{link-en|Kazimierz Kay-Skrzypeski|Kazimierz Kay-Skrzypeski}}後首位在冬奧會練習期間死亡的雪橇手。<ref>{{Citation|last = Wallechinsky|first = David|last2 = Loucky|first2 = Jaime|title = The Complete Book of the Winter Olympics: 2010 Edition|place = London|publisher = Aurum Press Limited|year = 2009|chapter = Luge (Toboggan): Men|page =158}}</ref>這也是雪橇運動在1975年後首次出現的致命事故。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Luge: Luge start moved as officials defend Whistler Sliding track.|publisher = VANOC|date = 2010-02-13|url = http://www.vancouver2010.com/olympic-news/n/news/afp-news/luge--luge-start-moved-as-officials-defend-whistler-sliding-track_274696sA.html|accessdate = 2010-02-13|archive-date = 2010-02-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100214125400/http://www.vancouver2010.com/olympic-news/n/news/afp-news/luge--luge-start-moved-as-officials-defend-whistler-sliding-track_274696sA.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>國際雪橇聯合會（FIL）、國際奧委會和溫哥華奧組委同日發表聯合聲明，就此表示深切遺憾，並宣佈取消當日餘下的訓練活動。<ref name=joint>{{Cite web|title = Joined Statement of IOC, FIL, and VANOC.|publisher = FIL|date = 2010-02-12|url = http://www.fil-luge.org/News-Detail.335.0.html?&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=11561&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=331&cHash=c1df2390c8|accessdate = 2010-02-13|archive-date = 2015-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924012725/http://www.fil-luge.org/News-Detail.335.0.html?&tx_ttnews[tt_news]=11561&tx_ttnews[backPid]=331&cHash=c1df2390c8|dead-url = no}}</ref>

賽道在16號彎位後的路段在事後加建障壁，冰層輪廓亦作修改。雪橇男子單人賽事亦改用女子單人和男子雙人賽事的出發點<ref>{{Cite web|title = Joint VANOC – FIL Statement on Men’s Luge Competition|publisher = VANOC|date = 2010-02-12|url = http://www.vancouver2010.com/olympic-news/n/news/fil-statement-on-mens-luge-competition_274462nE.html|accessdate = 2010-02-12|archive-date = 2010-12-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101225204821/http://www.vancouver2010.com/olympic-news/n/news/fil-statement-on-mens-luge-competition_274462nE.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，而後兩者則改用青年組的出發點。<ref name=rtr021410>{{Cite web |last = Herman|first = Martyn|title = Women sliders now have kids race – German.|publisher = Reuters|date = 2010-02-14|url = http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE61D2EQ20100214?feedType=RSS&feedName=everything&virtualBrandChannel=11563|accessdate = 2010-02-14}}.</ref>FIL秘書長羅姆斯塔德於2月14日表示會方於事後曾考慮取消雪橇賽事。<ref name=rtr021510>{{Cite web|last = Reich|first = Sharon|title = FIL considered cancelling competition|publisher = Reuters|date = 2010-02-15|url = http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE61E11120100215?feedType=RSS&feedName=everything&virtualBrandChannel=11563|accessdate = 2010-02-16}}</ref>FIL也與索契2014年奧組委合作，研究減低當地滑行中心賽道的速度。<ref name=rtr021510 />

