==安全問題==
庫瑪麗塔什維利的意外令各界關注冬奧會運動員的安全問題。<ref name=ap022210>{{Cite web|title = IOC to act on luge death tragedy.|work = Associated Press|publisher = Olympics-NOW.com|date = 2010-02-21|url = http://www.olympics-now.com/2010/02/21/ioc-to-act-on-luge-death-tragedy/|accessdate = 2010-08-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110714235716/http://www.olympics-now.com/2010/02/21/ioc-to-act-on-luge-death-tragedy/|archive-date = 2011-07-14|dead-url = yes}}</ref>截至2010年2月21日，場館共發生了30宗涉及雪橇和雪車項目的碰撞事故。<ref name=ap022210 />各界就如何保障運動員安全議論紛紛，包括將參賽資格提高、要求運動員在賽道上進行多次試航、和減低賽道時速。<ref name=ap022210 />2014年索契奧組委已表明當地滑行中心賽道的時速會較威士拿滑行中心少6-9公里。<ref name=ap022210 />FIBT總裁斯托利表示賽道設計師應在挑戰選手實力和顧及選手安全間取得平衡。<ref name=yhoo022010>{{Cite web| last = Withers| first = Tom| title = US bobsledder: Whistler track 'stupid fast'.| publisher = Yahoo! Sports| date = 2010-02-20| url = http://sports.yahoo.com/olympics/news?=txbobwomensbobsledrohb| accessdate = 2010-07-25| archive-date = 2018-08-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180827022250/https://sports.yahoo.com/olympics/news/?=txbobwomensbobsledrohb| dead-url = no}}</ref>而有賽道設計師則指新建場館賽道的保護牆應加高40-50釐米，但也指出要興建一個完全沒有意外風險的場館幾近沒有可能。<ref name=ap022210 />溫哥華奧組委則指場館賽道在奧運前已被使用超過30000次，而FIBT和FIL皆沒有發出危險警報。<ref name=ap022210 />[[國際奧委會|國際奧委會]]主席[[雅克·羅格|雅克·羅格]]則表示他會竭盡所能確保意外不會重演。<ref name=ap022210 />

FIL在2010年4月9日至11日開會後發表有關庫瑪麗塔什維利意外的20頁報告，<ref name=fil032510>{{Cite web|title = FIL Final Report to be published after the Commissions meetings.|publisher = FIL|date = 2010-03-25|url = http://www.fil-luge.org/News-Detail.155.0.html?&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=11637&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=307&cHash=7778c222d7|accessdate = 2010-03-27}}</ref>並於4月12日呈交國際奧委會。<ref name=report>{{Cite web|title = Official Report to the International Olympic Committee on the accident of Georgia athlete Nodar Kumaritashvili at Whistler Sliding Center on February 12, 2010 during official luge training for the XXI. Winter Olympics Games|publisher = FIL|date = 2010-04-12|url = http://www.fil-luge.org/fileadmin/user_upload/Documents/Sonstiges/FIL_Final_Report.pdf|accessdate = 2010-04-19|archive-date = 2015-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924012818/http://www.fil-luge.org/fileadmin/user_upload/Documents/Sonstiges/FIL_Final_Report.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Publication on Monday: FIL submit reports to IOC.|publisher = FIL|date = 2010-04-13|url = http://www.fil-luge.org/News-Detail.155.0.html?&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=11661&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=45&cHash=e51ef3e6b3|accessdate = 2010-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = FIL publishes Accident Report.|publisher = FIL|date = 2010-04-19|url = http://www.fil-luge.org/News-Detail.155.0.html?&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=11671&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=45&cHash=32aec05ba3|accessdate = 2010-04-19|archive-date = 2011-01-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110121130233/http://www.fil-luge.org/News-Detail.155.0.html?&tx_ttnews[tt_news]=11671&tx_ttnews[backPid]=45&cHash=32aec05ba3|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==場館設計及工程==
[[File:Whistler_Sliding_Centre-track_map_english.svg|thumb]]

場館工程預算原為5500萬加元，但工程費用最終達1億500萬元。<ref name=fil022309>{{Cite web|title = 153,98 km/h – new speed record at the "Whistler Sliding Center".|publisher = FIL|date = 2009-02-23|url = http://www.fil-luge.org/News-Detail.155.0.html?&tx_ttnews%5BpS%5D=1233442800&tx_ttnews%5BpL%5D=2419199&tx_ttnews%5Barc%5D=1&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=10387&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=157&cHash=602572b57f|accessdate = 2009-02-23}}</ref>賽道由鋼筋混凝土建成，重量達350[[公頓|公頓]]，<ref name=siteprep /><ref name=worker /><ref name=open2 />而賽道下的冷凍管道則全長100公里以上。<ref name=construct /><ref name=open2 />冰塊厚度為2-5釐米，並由人手操控。<ref name=open2 />賽道設有36個攝影機和42個計時器。<ref name=open2 />場館並包括控制塔和行政中心。<ref name=construct />

為了推廣可持續發展，場館設於既有滑雪區之側，以減低對鄰近生態環境的影響。賽道鬆上白色以便保持低溫和減低對冷凍系統的負荷，而冷凍系統的[[廢棄熱|廢棄熱]]則用作場館其他建築物的暖氣。工地平整產生的木廢料則製成[[堆肥|堆肥]]。<ref name=story>{{Cite web|title = Sustainability and legacy information on the site selection area for the Whistler Sliding Centre.|publisher = VANOC|url = http://www.vancouver2010.com/olympic-spectator-guide/venues/the-whistler-sliding-centre/sustainability---legacy/|accessdate = 2009-12-10|archive-date = 2009-12-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091223175208/http://www.vancouver2010.com/olympic-spectator-guide/venues/the-whistler-sliding-centre/sustainability---legacy/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

溫哥華奧組委於2006年為場館的冷凍房申請[[領先能源與環境設計|領先能源與環境設計]]（LEED）的銀色認證；冷凍房於2010年2月2日獲發金色認證。<ref>{{Cite web|title = The Whistler Sliding Centre Refrigeration Building.|publisher = Canada Green Building Council|url = http://www.cagbc.org/leed/leed_projects/registered_projects/building_registrations10381.php?project_city=Whistler&project_province=BC|accessdate = 2010-03-28|archive-date = 2019-02-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190201013604/https://www.cagbc.org//leed/leed_projects/registered_projects/building_registrations10381.php?project_city=Whistler&project_province=BC|dead-url = yes}}</ref>另外，場館亦於2008年獲卑詩已拌混凝土協會頒發兩項優秀混凝土建築獎項。<ref>{{Cite web|title = 2008 BC Awards for Excellence in Concrete Construction, including the Whistler Sliding Centre.|publisher = British Columbia Ready-Mixed Concrete Association|url = http://www.bcrmca.bc.ca/media/2008%20winners.pdf|accessdate = 2009-12-10|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110706165056/http://www.bcrmca.bc.ca/media/2008%20winners.pdf|archivedate = 2011-07-06}}</ref>

